Video Tutorial?? - It's hardly a video tutorial, I'd say it's more of a a video demonstration that is poorly done.  No audio, No description,  Just shows the some program text titles & then being opened using the run command.  Compelled enough to create a video but not enough to narrate it or provide a text description just seems like a waste of effort.
